</SO>
<CO>
   HQOSA HQOIA SPLS BZMT
</CO>
<IN>
SPECIALTY RETAILERS (OTS)
TENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM)
</IN>
<LP>
   HQ Office Supplies Warehouse Inc. said its board reached
"an agreement in principle" with its affiliate and former
subsidiary, HQ Office International Inc., to complete a
merger proposed on Sept. 4. The operator of office supply
stores currently owns 25% of HQ Office International.
   The transaction is subject to approval of the shareholders
of HQ Office International, regulatory approvals, and other
closing conditions. HQ Office Supplies said it expects the
merger will be completed in early 1991.
</LP>
