WESTERN U.S. BANKS (BAW)
BANKS (BNK)
</IN>
<LP>
   Ventura County National Bancorp, Oxnard, Calif., expects
to report net income for the fourth quarter of about
$698,000, or 13 cents a share, on revenue of about $9.4
million, W.E. McAleer, president and chief executive officer,
